{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781423102966,"sessionID":"ses_13ae9b23fffe3MGENYGODNFHfK","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_03_TnJI8g77c88RsYIrYJvj3770","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/review/reorg-verify/lineages/deepseek/deep-review-strategy.md","content":"# Deep Review Strategy - Session Tracking\n\n## 1. TOPIC\nReorg verification review of 027-xce-research-based-refinement phase-parent reorganization\n\n## 2. REVIEW DIMENSIONS (remaining)\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n- [ ] D1 Correctness, Logic errors, off-by-one, wrong return types, broken invariants\n- [ ] D2 Security, Injection, auth bypass, secrets exposure, unsafe deserialization\n- [ ] D3 Traceability, Spec/code alignment, checklist evidence, cross-reference integrity\n- [ ] D4 Maintainability, Patterns, clarity, documentation quality, safe follow-on change cost\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n## 3. NON-GOALS\n- Re-implementing any phase child work\n- Deep code review of system-spec-kit implementation code\n- Assessing the quality of child-phase implementation changes\n\n## 4. STOP CONDITIONS\n- All 4 dimensions converged with no new P0/P1 findings for 2 consecutive iterations\n- Max 5 iterations reached\n- Any confirmed P0 finding that cannot be resolved\n\n## 5. COMPLETED DIMENSIONS\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n[None yet]\n\n| Dimension | Verdict | Iteration | Summary |\n|-----------|---------|-----------|---------|\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n## 6. RUNNING FINDINGS\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n- **P0 (Critical):** 0 active\n- **P1 (Major):** 0 active\n- **P2 (Minor):** 0 active\n- **Delta this iteration:** +0 P0, +0 P1, +0 P2\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n## 7. WHAT WORKED\n[First iteration -- populated after iteration 1 completes]\n\n## 8. WHAT FAILED\n[First iteration -- populated after iteration 1 completes]\n\n## 9. EXHAUSTED APPROACHES (do not retry)\n[None yet]\n\n## 10. RULED OUT DIRECTIONS\n[None yet]\n\n## 11. NEXT FOCUS\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\nD1 Correctness: Verify phase-parent spec structure integrity — check spec.md Phase Documentation Map entries match actual child folders on disk, validate context-index.md old-to-new path bridge accuracy, check graph-metadata.json child pointers\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n## 12. KNOWN CONTEXT\nResource-map.md is present at the spec folder root (27 entries across Skills=16, Specs=11). The phase parent groups 30 former top-level phases under 6 themed tracks (000-005). context-index.md provides the old-to-new path bridge. The `before-vs-after.md` narrates the epic by system. graph-metadata.json stores derived status and child pointers.\n\n## 13. CROSS-REFERENCE STATUS\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n| Protocol | Level | Status | Iteration | Notes |\n|----------|-------|--------|-----------|-------|\n| `spec_code` | core | pending | - | |\n| `checklist_evidence` | core | pending | - | |\n| `feature_catalog_code` | overlay | pending | - | |\n| `playbook_capability` | overlay | pending | - | |\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n## 14. FILES UNDER REVIEW\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n| File | Dimensions Reviewed | Last Iteration | Findings | Status |\n|------|-------------------|----------------|----------|--------|\n| spec.md | - | - | - | pending |\n| context-index.md | - | - | - | pending |\n| graph-metadata.json | - | - | - | pending |\n| description.json | - | - | - | pending |\n| resource-map.md | - | - | - | pending |\n| before-vs-after.md | - | - | - | pending |\n| timeline.md | - | - | - | pending |\n| handover.md | - | - | - | pending |\n| 000-release-cleanup/ | - | - | - | pending |\n| 001-research-and-doctrine/ | - | - | - | pending |\n| 002-memory-store-and-search/ | - | - | - | pending |\n| 003-advisor-and-codegraph/ | - | - | - | pending |\n| 004-shared-infrastructure/ | - | - | - | pending |\n| 005-verification-and-remediation/ | - | - | - | pending |\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n## 15. REVIEW BOUNDARIES\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n- Max iterations: 5\n- Convergence threshold: 0.10\n- Rolling STOP threshold: 0.08\n- No-progress threshold: 0.05\n- Coverage stabilization passes required: 1\n- Session lineage: sessionId=fanout-deepseek-1781423033387-5rmxex, parentSessionId=null, generation=1, lineageMode=new\n- Findings registry: deep-review-findings-registry.json\n- Release-readiness states: in-progress | converged | release-blocking\n- Per-iteration budget: 12 tool calls, 10 minutes\n- Severity threshold: P2\n- Review target type: spec-folder\n- Cross-reference checks: core=[spec_code,checklist_evidence], overlay=[feature_catalog_code,playbook_capability]\n- resource_map_present: true\n- Started: 2026-06-14T00:00:00Z\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/review/reorg-verify/lineages/deepseek/deep-review-strategy.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/review/reorg-verify/lineages/deepseek/deep-review-strategy.md","time":{"start":1781423102962,"end":1781423102965}},"id":"prt_ec5172d45001C5Z2aneUqqZ57s","sessionID":"ses_13ae9b23fffe3MGENYGODNFHfK","messageID":"msg_ec516f310001mkyGx6Bo7j4tEm"}}
