{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781423204604,"sessionID":"ses_13ae9b23fffe3MGENYGODNFHfK","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_01_KePKtWtlULKmXF5Erjn21545","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Deep Review Strategy - Session Tracking\n\n## 1. TOPIC\nReorg verification review of 027-xce-research-based-refinement phase-parent reorganization\n\n## 2. REVIEW DIMENSIONS (remaining)\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n- [x] D1 Correctness — CONDITIONAL (2 P1, 2 P2)\n- [ ] D2 Security, Injection, auth bypass, secrets exposure, unsafe deserialization\n- [ ] D3 Traceability, Spec/code alignment, checklist evidence, cross-reference integrity\n- [ ] D4 Maintainability, Patterns, clarity, documentation quality, safe follow-on change cost\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n## 3. NON-GOALS\n- Re-implementing any phase child work\n- Deep code review of system-spec-kit implementation code\n- Assessing the quality of child-phase implementation changes\n\n## 4. STOP CONDITIONS\n- All 4 dimensions converged with no new P0/P1 findings for 2 consecutive iterations\n- Max 5 iterations reached\n- Any confirmed P0 finding that cannot be resolved\n\n## 5. COMPLETED DIMENSIONS\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n| Dimension | Verdict | Iteration | Summary |\n|-----------|---------|-----------|---------|\n| D1 Correctness | CONDITIONAL | 1 | 2 P1 (stale key_files path, stale resource-map) + 2 P2 (description.json issues). Phase map matches disk. |\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n## 6. RUNNING FINDINGS\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n- **P0 (Critical):** 0 active\n- **P1 (Major):** 2 active (F001, F002)\n- **P2 (Minor):** 2 active (F003, F004)\n- **Delta this iteration:** +0 P0, +2 P1, +2 P2\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n## 7. WHAT WORKED\n- Cross-referencing spec.md Phase Documentation Map against actual disk folders: quick verification with Glob\n- Spot-checking context-index.md bridge entries: 5/5 resolved correctly\n- Combining multiple state files in one read cycle for efficient scope discovery\n\n## 8. WHAT FAILED\n[None yet]\n\n## 9. EXHAUSTED APPROACHES (do not retry)\n[None yet]\n\n## 10. RULED OUT DIRECTIONS\n- context-index.md bridge inaccuracy: All spot-checked entries resolve to existing files on disk (iteration 1)\n- spec.md phase map / folder mismatch: All 6 tracks have matching folders with spec.md present (iteration 1)\n\n## 11. NEXT FOCUS\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\nD2 Security: Scan spec docs, template references, and metadata files for secrets exposure, unsafe file paths, and injection risks in the reorganized phase parent structure. Focus on resource-map.md skill paths, handover.md command examples, and context-index.md path references.\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n## 12. KNOWN CONTEXT\nResource-map.md is present at the spec folder root (27 entries across Skills=16, Specs=11). The phase parent groups 30 former top-level phases under 6 themed tracks (000-005). context-index.md provides the old-to-new path bridge. The `before-vs-after.md` narrates the epic by system. graph-metadata.json stores derived status and child pointers.\n\n## 13. CROSS-REFERENCE STATUS\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n| Protocol | Level | Status | Iteration | Notes |\n|----------|-------|--------|-----------|-------|\n| `spec_code` | core | partial | 1 | Phase map matches disk (6/6); 2 metadata drift issues found (F001, F002) |\n| `checklist_evidence` | core | pending | - | |\n| `feature_catalog_code` | overlay | pending | - | |\n| `playbook_capability` | overlay | pending | - | |\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n## 14. FILES UNDER REVIEW\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n| File | Dimensions Reviewed | Last Iteration | Findings | Status |\n|------|-------------------|----------------|----------|--------|\n| spec.md | D1 | 1 | 0 P0, 0 P1, 0 P2 | complete |\n| context-index.md | D1 | 1 | 0 P0, 0 P1, 0 P2 | complete |\n| graph-metadata.json | D1 | 1 | 0 P0, 1 P1, 0 P2 | partial |\n| description.json | D1 | 1 | 0 P0, 0 P1, 2 P2 | partial |\n| resource-map.md | D1 | 1 | 0 P0, 1 P1, 0 P2 | partial |\n| before-vs-after.md | D1 | 1 | 0 P0, 0 P1, 0 P2 | complete |\n| timeline.md | D1 | 1 | 0 P0, 0 P1, 0 P2 | complete |\n| handover.md | D1 | 1 | 0 P0, 0 P1, 0 P2 | complete |\n| 000-release-cleanup/ | - | - | - | pending |\n| 001-research-and-doctrine/ | - | - | - | pending |\n| 002-memory-store-and-search/ | - | - | - | pending |\n| 003-advisor-and-codegraph/ | - | - | - | pending |\n| 004-shared-infrastructure/ | - | - | - | pending |\n| 005-verification-and-remediation/ | - | - | - | pending |\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n## 15. REVIEW BOUNDARIES\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n- Max iterations: 5\n- Convergence threshold: 0.10\n- Rolling STOP threshold: 0.08\n- No-progress threshold: 0.05\n- Coverage stabilization passes required: 1\n- Session lineage: sessionId=fanout-deepseek-1781423033387-5rmxex, parentSessionId=null, generation=1, lineageMode=new\n- Findings registry: deep-review-findings-registry.json\n- Release-readiness states: in-progress | converged | release-blocking\n- Per-iteration budget: 12 tool calls, 10 minutes\n- Severity threshold: P2\n- Review target type: spec-folder\n- Cross-reference checks: core=[spec_code,checklist_evidence], overlay=[feature_catalog_code,playbook_capability]\n- resource_map_present: true\n- Started: 2026-06-14T00:00:00Z\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/review/reorg-verify/lineages/deepseek/deep-review-strategy.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/review/reorg-verify/lineages/deepseek/deep-review-strategy.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/review/reorg-verify/lineages/deeps