{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781423208137,"sessionID":"ses_13ae9b23fffe3MGENYGODNFHfK","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_02_ReVvKyiKlJGV44xNdbsE6411","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Deep Review Dashboard\n\n## Status\n- Verdict: CONDITIONAL (2 P1 active)\n- hasAdvisories: true\n- Iteration: 1/5\n- Status: running\n\n## Findings Summary\n- P0 (Critical): 0 active\n- P1 (Major): 2 active (F001, F002)\n- P2 (Minor): 2 active (F003, F004)\n- Delta: +0 P0, +2 P1, +2 P2\n\n## Progress Table\n| Iteration | Focus | Status | Dimensions | Ratio | Findings |\n|-----------|-------|--------|------------|-------|----------|\n| 1 | D1 Correctness | complete | correctness | 0.75 | 0 P0, 2 P1, 2 P2 |\n\n## Dimension Coverage\n| Dimension | Status |\n|-----------|--------|\n| D1 Correctness | done (CONDITIONAL) |\n| D2 Security | pending |\n| D3 Traceability | pending |\n| D4 Maintainability | pending |\n\n## Trend\n| Iteration | Ratio |\n|-----------|-------|\n| 1 | 0.75 |\n\nDirection: N/A (first iteration). Rolling average: 0.75.\n\n## Active Risks\n- 2 P1 findings active (F001: stale key_files path, F002: stale resource-map)\n- High newFindingsRatio (0.75) — expected for first iteration\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/review/reorg-verify/lineages/deepseek/deep-review-dashboard.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/review/reorg-verify/lineages/deepseek/deep-review-dashboard.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/review/reorg-verify/lineages/deepseek/deep-review-dashboard.md","time":{"start":1781423208130,"end":1781423208136}},"id":"prt_ec518e944001CIzMIZr9WRwukk","sessionID":"ses_13a